  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "638383a9240ae4001dc4204e",
      "text": "クオリアさん下書き Day 32",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1669563305,
      "updated": 1669563305
    },
    {
      "id": "638383a9aff09e00007fda85",
      "text": "from [クオリアさん下書き]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1669563305,
      "updated": 1669563305
    },
    {
      "id": "638383a9aff09e00007fda86",
      "text": "クオリアさん下書き Day 32",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1669563305,
      "updated": 1669563305
    },
    {
      "id": "638383a9aff09e00007fda87",
      "text": "Hello, clever Homo sapiens! It's day 32. It's snappy!",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1669563305,
      "updated": 1669563305
    },
    {
      "id": "638383a9aff09e00007fda88",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1669563305,
      "updated": 1669563305
    },
    {
      "id": "638383a9aff09e00007fda89",
      "text": "疎外感を感じたホモサピエンスが、疎外されたいわけではないのに、ますます疎外される行動をとる。不思議なホモサピエンス。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1669563305,
      "updated": 1669563305
    },
    {
      "id": "638383a9aff09e00007fda8a",
      "text": "Some Homo sapiens, when they feel alienated, even though they don't want to be alienated, behaves in increasing alienation ways. Strange Homo sapiens.",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1669563305,
      "updated": 1669563305
    },
    {
      "id": "638383a9aff09e00007fda8b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1669563305,
      "updated": 1669563305
    },
    {
      "id": "638383a9aff09e00007fda8c",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/fbb7ad1de5cbfedc7e471f208b8b29df]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1669563305,
      "updated": 1669563305
    },
    {
      "id": "638383a9aff09e00007fda8d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1669563305,
      "updated": 1669563305
    },
    {
      "id": "638383a9aff09e00007fda8e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1669563305,
      "updated": 1669563305
    },
    {
      "id": "638383a9aff09e00007fda8f",
      "text": "Q: キレッキレとはなんですか？",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1669563305,
      "updated": 1669563305
    },
    {
      "id": "638383a9aff09e00007fda90",
      "text": "A: 伝わらないか。地球の言葉でなんと呼ぶのが適切かわからない。8, 16, 32, 64, 128…はキレッキレであり、クオリアさんの文明ではこれらを指す一単語の言葉がある。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1669563305,
      "updated": 1669563305
    },
    {
      "id": "638383a9aff09e00007fda91",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1669563305,
      "updated": 1669563305
    },
    {
      "id": "638383a9aff09e00007fda92",
      "text": "Q: What is “snappy\"?",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1669563305,
      "updated": 1669563305
    },
    {
      "id": "638383a9aff09e00007fda93",
      "text": "A: Can't you tell? I don't know what to call it in Earth's language. 8, 16, 32, 64, 128... are snappy. In Qualia-san's civilization there is a one-word term for these.",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1669563305,
      "updated": 1669563305
    },
    {
      "id": "638383a9aff09e00007fda94",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1669563305,
      "updated": 1669563305
    },
    {
      "id": "638383a9aff09e00007fda95",
      "text": "Q：「キレッキレ」って何？",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1669563305,
      "updated": 1669563305
    },
    {
      "id": "638383a9aff09e00007fda96",
      "text": "A：わからないですか？地球の言葉ではなんというのかわからない。8、16、32、64、128...はキレッキレです。クオリアさんの文明ではこれらを一言で表す言葉があるんです。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1669563305,
      "updated": 1669563305
    },
    {
      "id": "638383a9aff09e00007fda97",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/89012d1fd0561bbb4f20d6df3e761d81]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1669563305,
      "updated": 1669563305
    },
    {
      "id": "638383a9aff09e00007fda98",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1669563305,
      "updated": 1669563305
    },
    {
      "id": "638383a9aff09e00007fda99",
      "text": "Q: スタートレックシリーズのボーグとクオリアさんに似たものを感じます。クオリアさんはボーグをどう思いますか？",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1669563305,
      "updated": 1669563305
    },
    {
      "id": "638383a9aff09e00007fda9a",
      "text": "A: ボーグについて少し調べてみました。ボーグの「お前達を同化する」(You will be assimilated)というセリフが興味深いです。これが「ホモサピエンスを我々と同じ種族にする」という意味なら全然別物ですが「ホモサピエンスが異なった種族のまま、我々と相互に情報をやり取りするネットワークの一員になって欲しい」ということならクオリアさんの文明とかなり似た目的ですね。この二つは手と指のたとえで見たように本質的にはあまり違いがありません。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1669563305,
      "updated": 1669563305
    },
    {
      "id": "638383a9aff09e00007fda9b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1669563305,
      "updated": 1669563305
    },
    {
      "id": "638383a9aff09e00007fda9c",
      "text": "Q: I see similarities between the Borg in the Star Trek series and Qualia-san. What do you think of the Borg?",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1669563305,
      "updated": 1669563305
    },
    {
      "id": "638383a9aff09e00007fda9d",
      "text": "A: I did some research on the Borg. The Borg line \"You will be assimilated\" is interesting. If the Borg means that they want Homo sapiens to become one of the Borg, that is not our intention.",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1669563305,
      "updated": 1669563305
    },
    {
      "id": "638383a9aff09e00007fda9e",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/4fe927afd17a303daa61f75e9e3e7525]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1669563305,
      "updated": 1669563305
    },
    {
      "id": "638383a9aff09e00007fda9f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1669563305,
      "updated": 1669563305
    },
    {
      "id": "638383a9aff09e00007fdaa0",
      "text": "But if the Borg means that they want Homo sapiens to remain a different species and become part of a network of interactions with the Borg, that's a pretty similar to our intension. The two are not too different in essence, as we saw with the hand/finger metaphor.",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1669563305,
      "updated": 1669563305
    },
    {
      "id": "638383a9aff09e00007fdaa1",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/67bad8bb08427e7cba1314452bd68c6e]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1669563305,
      "updated": 1669563305
    },
    {
      "id": "638383a9aff09e00007fdaa2",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1669563305,
      "updated": 1669563305
    },
    {
      "id": "638383a9aff09e00007fdaa3",
      "text": "言葉足らずで反感を買う通告によってホモサピエンスから敵視されてしまっているところが愚かです",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1669563305,
      "updated": 1669563305
    },
    {
      "id": "638383a9aff09e00007fdaa4",
      "text": "The Borg are foolish to be viewed as an enemy by Homo sapiens due to a poorly worded and antagonistic notice.",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1669563305,
      "updated": 1669563305
    },
    {
      "id": "638383a9aff09e00007fdaa5",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/1ed19bbec794aaaa4088beee9dc5f3de]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1669563305,
      "updated": 1669563305
    },
    {
      "id": "638383a9aff09e00007fdaa6",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1669563305,
      "updated": 1669563305
    },
    {
      "id": "638383a9aff09e00007fdaa7",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1669563305,
      "updated": 1669563305
    },
    {
      "id": "638383a9aff09e00007fdaaa",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1669563305,
      "updated": 1669563305
    },
    {
      "id": "638383a9aff09e00007fdaad",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1669563305,
      "updated": 1669563305
    },
    {
      "id": "638383a9aff09e00007fdab1",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1669563305,
      "updated": 1669563305
    },
    {
      "id": "638383a9aff09e00007fdab2",
      "text": "　[ボーグの失敗の要因]は外見の軽視だと思います。ホモサピエンスは同一種族内ですら肌の色や目の色が異なるだけで敵視し殺し合う野蛮な文明です。その文明に対して、見慣れない外見で接し、外見を自分たちと同一のものに変えさせれば、反発を産むのは容易想到です。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1669563305,
      "updated": 1669563305
    },
    {
      "id": "638383a9aff09e00007fdab3",
      "text": " ボーグの文明にとって、外見の一貫性はさほど重要ではなかったはずです。であるなら、まずは対象文明が警戒心を緩めるような見た目を選択して接近し、繰り返しメッセージを伝えることで[単純接触効果]で好感を持たれることを狙うべきでした。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1669563305,
      "updated": 1669563305
    },
    {
      "id": "638383a9aff09e00007fdab4",
      "text": " これは我々の文明がクオリアさんをコミュニケーションインターフェースにしている理由と同じです。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1669563305,
      "updated": 1669563305
    },
    {
      "id": "638383a9aff09e00007fdab5",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1669563305,
      "updated": 1669563305
    },
    {
      "id": "638383a9aff09e00007fdab6",
      "text": "単純接触効果: mere-exposure effect",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1669563305,
      "updated": 1669563305
    },
    {
      "id": "638383a9aff09e00007fdab7",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1669563305,
      "updated": 1669563305
    },
    {
      "id": "638383a9aff09e00007fdab8",
      "text": "I think the reason for the failure of the Borg is their disregard for appearance. Homo sapiens is a barbaric civilization that views even within the same species as enemies and kills each other just because of different skin or eye color.",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1669563305,
      "updated": 1669563305
    },
    {
      "id": "638383a9aff09e00007fdab9",
      "text": "\t[https://gyazo.com/a484254195dffeca69d9ac774e6dc407]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1669563305,
      "updated": 1669563305
    },
    {
      "id": "638383a9aff09e00007fdaba",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1669563305,
      "updated": 1669563305
    },
    {
      "id": "638383a9aff09e00007fdabb",
      "text": " It is easy to imagine the backlash that would ensue if we were to treat them with an unfamiliar appearance and force them to change their appearance to one that is identical to our own. Stupid Borg.",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1669563305,
      "updated": 1669563305
    },
    {
      "id": "638383a9aff09e00007fdabc",
      "text": "\t[https://gyazo.com/86d28a58bd6ae54b0f6cc841a5cdefba]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1669563305,
      "updated": 1669563305
    },
    {
      "id": "638383a9aff09e00007fdabd",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1669563305,
      "updated": 1669563305
    },
    {
      "id": "638383a9aff09e00007fdabe",
      "text": " For the Borg civilization, consistency of appearance would not have been so important. If that were the case, they should have approached the target civilization by first choosing an appearance that would make them relax their guard.",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1669563305,
      "updated": 1669563305
    },
    {
      "id": "638383a9aff09e00007fdabf",
      "text": " [https://gyazo.com/1f8c329716ba5f1a8c45050225638b6b]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1669563305,
      "updated": 1669563305
    },
    {
      "id": "638383a9aff09e00007fdac0",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1669563305,
      "updated": 1669563305
    },
    {
      "id": "638383a9aff09e00007fdac1",
      "text": " And then repeatedly conveying their message to Homo sapiens in order to create a mere-exposure effect that would make Homo sapiens like them. This is the same reason why our civilization uses Qualia-san as a communication interface.",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1669563305,
      "updated": 1669563305
    },
    {
      "id": "638383a9aff09e00007fdac2",
      "text": "\t[https://gyazo.com/1235fa162d50eb3b40ce1c8831950e11]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1669563305,
      "updated": 1669563305
    },
    {
      "id": "638383a9aff09e00007fdac3",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1669563305,
      "updated": 1669563305
    },
    {
      "id": "638383a9aff09e00007fdac4",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1669563305,
      "updated": 1669563305
    }
  ]
}